<h1>Hotel <span class='highlight'>Corsendonk Duinse Polders</span></h1>
	Just outside of the city, nestled between the dunes and the <span class='highlight'>Zeebos</span> (a lovely park between forest and sea), the <span class='highlight'>Duinse Polders</span> is a calm and well-equipped vacation center with an easy access and lovely surroundings.
	<br/>
	It has a mini-golf course, a big playground, several sport fields (tennis, volleyball and basketball) and happens to be located a hundred meters away from <span class='highlight'>SeaLife</span>, a park dedicated to underwater fauna.	<div class="vspace"></div>
	The hotel has free parking and provides free wifi in the studios as well as the event rooms.	
	<div class="vspace"></div>
